title: Alldata v10.40 w Domestic Disc 3 1982-2011
description:
I'm uploading this for comments I've read. Either people didn't want to download the whole program, didn't have enough disc space, or just wanted 1 disc for the vehicle they drive. Enjoy Mates!

With ALLDATA Repair, you have instant access to a single source of accurate, up-to-date OE-direct diagnosis, repair, and maintenance information. Our huge database offers you information covering more than 33,000 engine-specific vehicles. Repair procedures, diagrams and TSBs are specific to each vehicle for fast, factory-correct repairs. Your customers will appreciate knowing that your repairs meet manufacturer standards.
